{"tid":1607093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[情報戰]咁做或者可以救到好多人","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:35.000Z","uid":225916,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4627c7e61d9504870cbfef2175c2593617e66427","tid":1607093,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:34:16.000Z","msg":"你哋仲記唔記得小巴佬篤灰單嘢<br />\n仲有好多單 狗上樓搜屋<br />\n點解？？？點解有手足俾人拉？？好簡單 就係有啲仆街篤灰<br />\n而情報又十分準確<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日 如果大家見到有啲地方<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">貌似</span>有啲暴力分子出現，例如有幾個操福建口音嘅人士 或者<span style=\"color: red;\">你可能聽錯佢哋想打人</span>喎 <br />\n你已經可以報警<br />\n又或者見到巴士有幾個面目猙獰<br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">無意間可能聽錯 以為佢哋係暴徒嘅時候</span><br />\n一定要篤灰<br />\n總之<span style=\"color: red;\"> 錯誤情報 愈多愈好</span><br />\n可以玩9啲廢老聚集嘅地方呀<br />\n等班狗周圍搜，將假情報混入去<br />\n首先搜完一輪乜都冇，佢哋就會燥底<br />\n隨時郁手打柒啲廢老<br />\n一嚟 擾民 可以借刀搞9藍絲廢老，二嚟 令佢哋捉唔到咁多手足 因為情報冇咁精準 令佢哋工作量倍增<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知我講得1999 <br />\n可唔可以幫我推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a597cb2b2e68e2915b9bd6ca169eedaabe8b55d8","tid":1607093,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"CHING SICK BALL<br />\n山頂警署護旗手madam叫大家打俾佢喎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607090</a>"},{"pid":"2c231d1d91a06eb01836814a93fd6e145c055207","tid":1607093,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa9dad94e3df1e72a8033e16553231bb7e24a0ac","tid":1607093,"uid":225916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a597cb2b2e68e2915b9bd6ca169eedaabe8b55d8","tid":1607093,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"CHING SICK BALL<br />\n山頂警署護旗手madam叫大家打俾佢喎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607090</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"大家好似忽略咗哩招<br />\n到時要不停放流料俾對家<br />\n等佢分唔清真假"},{"pid":"497bef931e662acf4bdba96b7b2e8de240511e6e","tid":1607093,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"推上去呀"},{"pid":"49bc177d175658390b2bb4e3941c2a607780c9e0","tid":1607093,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"999佢地仲會理咩..."},{"pid":"787350531791fd541bb9405c2cea8b0136ac2674","tid":1607093,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:43:18.000Z","msg":"對家咁鍾意用流料<br />\n我哋就用返流料對付返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44dacf6ba5526ffc7532b7d3c045e47420fa74a4","tid":1607093,"uid":14494,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"49bc177d175658390b2bb4e3941c2a607780c9e0","tid":1607093,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"999佢地仲會理咩..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"你話有班黑衫實理, 當然要有番咁上下年紀鄉音既人去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔洗999, 係藍屍D谷度放都得"},{"pid":"a31418e662c0d3df1007e04be9e30f605887a433","tid":1607093,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34028d202849357e3f261ae073f38341a9f6fbf1","tid":1607093,"uid":225916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"44dacf6ba5526ffc7532b7d3c045e47420fa74a4","tid":1607093,"uid":14494,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"49bc177d175658390b2bb4e3941c2a607780c9e0","tid":1607093,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"999佢地仲會理咩..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"你話有班黑衫實理, 當然要有番咁上下年紀鄉音既人去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔洗999, 係藍屍D谷度放都得"},